race.comment: OHH ERROL (7) broke the maiden status at Townsville when having his first run for the new stable and will have derived a stack of confidence from that victory. Gets in well at the weights with the 3kg claim and can go back-to-back without surprising. VICTORY'S GHOST (3) is a two-time winner here who will be ready to peak now fourth-up from the spell. Certainly can make his presence felt in the small field. THE LAST SAGA (8) saves his best form for this seven-furlong journey and may earn some minor money. OUR HEART THROB (14) draws the inside alley and is next in line in a race decimated by scratchings.
